name: INQUISITION_APOCALYPSE #7
description:
This is the last piece of a series called INQUISITION, a series I created to talk about art, which is constantly morphing. But some people just don’t get it, it doesn’t matter if they’re young or old, progressive or conservative, artists or not. 

In this world I created, these people have won. They hunt and killed every creative thinker and true artist, and destroyed some of the most disruptive and inovative art pieces that has ever existed.

But art will always rise from the ashes.
